  <div class="tip-overview text-content">
    <h4>Overview</h4>
    <h1 class="summary-rec">Reduce the size of files sent from your server to increase the speed to which they
are transferred to the browser.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Reduce sizes of pages by up to 70%</li>
  <li>Increase page speed</li>
  <li>Cost-benefit ratio: high</li>
  <li>Access needed to the .htaccess files or server administration files</li>
</ul>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="tip-analyze">
  <form action="/analyze.html" method="post">
    How does your site score on this rule?
